The location is unbeatable - less than a block away from Venice Beach - and the balcony had a great view of the beach (it helped that the weather was great).	The hotel was clean, the AC was cold, the view of the boardwalk and ocean from the small outdoor space was fantastic.	The hotel was clean and well maintained, the staff were attentive and sincerely interested in guests being happy, and the location (a block from Venice Beach) was perfect.	We survived the cold for one drink and a panini, but even so, this is a great place to enjoy the ocean view.